::Squizzy::

Squizzy smiles. "Don't mention it. Its my job."

She turns around and exits the room. "Now get some sleep," she says, 
closing the door behind her and going back to the lab. A thought 
suddenly pops into her head.

"Oh my gosh, Zergling!" she exclaims, realizing that the bot had been 
stuck in the CR chamber for several months now. She takes off at a 
run back to the lab.
